                    <h2>You + Nissan CARE</h2>
					<div class="thumb"><img src="/images/youPlus.gif" alt="You + Nissan Care" /></div>
                    <p>You are at the heart of everything we do and that's why we're committed to offering the best customer service on the market - You + Nissan CARE. Centred on five commitments, it gives you real benefits, like keeping you mobile, resolving your problems promptly and offering you continuous roadside assistance.</p>
					<p></p>

					<p><strong>You</strong> care about having your problems resolved quickly.<br />
					<strong>Nissan</strong> will propose how to resolve any problem within two working days.</p>

					<p><strong>You</strong> care about quality enough to have your Nissan serviced at a Nissan dealership.<br />
					<strong>Nissan</strong> says thanks by giving you continuous Nissan Roadside Assistance for free.</p>

					<p><strong>You</strong> care about getting the right Nissan model, engine and gearbox to test drive.<br />
					<strong>Nissan</strong> will guarantee that's what you'll get when you pre-book your test drive either online or through our customer service centre.</p>

					<p><strong>You</strong> care about getting the best value for money when it comes to service and repair.<br />
					<strong>Nissan</strong> will price match like for like competitor written quotes within 10 miles of your local dealer.</p>

					<p><strong>You</strong> care about staying on the road when your Nissan is in for service or repair.<br />
					<strong>Nissan</strong> will keep you mobile free of charge.</p>

					<p>If you'd like to find out more simply <a href="/our-services/nissan-care/" title="Find Out More">click here.</a></p>

